About Highlands
55+ Active Living in Ideal Central Florida Mobile Home Community!
Situated in Central Florida’s Lakeland area, Highlands Mobile Home Park is an affordable age-restricted mobile home community with 65 lots and a variety of local activities to compliment all lifestyles.
Surrounded by beautiful lakes, gardens, and wildlife preserves, nature enthusiasts have the choice of many outdoor attractions to explore. Clermont is also perfect for golfers of any skill-level as it is home to a number of pristine golf courses.
Explore local attractions such as the
Florida Citrus Tower
where you can view the beautiful city of Clermont from 226 feet up on an observation deck. Or stroll through
Historic Downtown Clermont
to enjoy live music, fine dining, the Sunday Farmer’s Market and local boutiques.
Theme Parks
Visit world-renown theme parks in Orlando such as Disney World, Sea World, Universal Studios and Discovery Cove.
Beaches
Florida’s warm, sandy west coast beaches are just a short drive away.
Area Golf
Pristine golf and country clubs are located all throughout the area, so you have plenty of courses to choose from to fit your game.
Lakeridge Winery
Visit Florida’s largest premium winery with over 110,000 visitors each year.
Parks and Rec
If you love the beauty of nature, the parks of Lake County offer a wide variety of scenery and activities to keep you busy year round. From dog parks, to blueways, to trails, to bird watching, your home in Timber Village is just your launching pad.
Museum and Arts
Take a trip to the President’s Hall of Fame or take a short trip to one of the local historic/art museums in Clermont or Orlando.
